name: Midnight Traverse
description: After successfully establishing contact, our hero heads out to the rendezvous point where the ascent pod awaits for the return to Earth. The effects of the toxic spores are wearing off but something still appears to be off...This is the follow up to "INTENSE ENCOUNTERS" and the third chapter of "Expedition", an exploratory adventure series of lens based cinemagraphs that build a narrative of adventure and early exploring, with retro sci-fi vibes and surreal overtones. Shot on location in the andean region of "Quebrada de las Señoritas".
